<div class="overflow-hidden bg-white py-24 sm:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 sm:gap-y-20 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="lg:pr-8 lg:pt-4">
        <div class="lg:max-w-lg">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-indigo-600">You want to become a guide?</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">That's Amazing!</p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600">Earn some extra money while having the time of your life by sharing your unique perspective of the things you love.</p>
          <dl class="mt-10 max-w-xl space-y-8 text-base leading-7 text-gray-600 lg:max-w-none">
            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                <svg class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5.5 17a4.5 4.5 0 01-1.44-8.765 4.5 4.5 0 018.302-3.046 3.5 3.5 0 014.504 4.272A4 4 0 0115 17H5.5zm3.75-2.75a.75.75 0 001.5 0V9.66l1.95 2.1a.75.75 0 101.1-1.02l-3.25-3.5a.75.75 0 00-1.1 0l-3.25 3.5a.75.75 0 101.1 1.02l1.95-2.1v4.59z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Let's get started.
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">You'll first need to navigate to your accounts page and create a new account <%= link_to "here", new_account_path, class: "rounded bg-indigo-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-indigo-600 shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-100"%>. Make sure you select "guide" as the customer type.</dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                <svg class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 1a4.5 4.5 0 00-4.5 4.5V9H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2h-.5V5.5A4.5 4.5 0 0010 1zm3 8V5.5a3 3 0 10-6 0V9h6z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Some follow up items.
              </dt>
              <% if current_account %>
              <dd class="inline">You'll need to complete a few tasks after your initial account creation. First, you'll need to set a location for your account, so go ahead and <%= link_to "navigate to edit your account", edit_account_path(current_account), class: "rounded bg-indigo-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-indigo-600 shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-100"%> for your guide account and set your operating location. This will make you available in that location. Additionally, you'll want to add some branding and details about what type of guide you are. Also, you'll want to create any tours you want to offer.</dd>
              <% else %>
              <dd class="inline">You'll need to complete a few tasks after your initial account creation. First, you'll need to set a location for your account, so go ahead and <%= link_to "navigate to edit your account", new_user_session_path, class: "rounded bg-indigo-50 px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-indigo-600 shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-100"%> for your guide account and set your operating location. This will make you available in that location. Additionally, you'll want to add some branding and details about what type of guide you are. Also, you'll want to create any tours you want to offer.</dd>
              <% end %>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-9">
              <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="absolute left-1 top-1 h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.516 2.17a.75.75 0 00-1.032 0 11.209 11.209 0 01-7.877 3.08.75.75 0 00-.722.515A12.74 12.74 0 002.25 9.75c0 5.942 4.064 10.933 9.563 12.348a.749.749 0 00.374 0c5.499-1.415 9.563-6.406 9.563-12.348 0-1.39-.223-2.73-.635-3.985a.75.75 0 00-.722-.516l-.143.001c-2.996 0-5.717-1.17-7.734-3.08zm3.094 8.016a.75.75 0 10-1.22-.872l-3.236 4.53L9.53 12.22a.75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06l2.25 2.25a.75.75 0 001.14-.094l3.75-5.25z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
                Going Live.
              </dt>
              <dd class="inline">In order to actually make your account go live, you'll need to get it approved, first. This can take several days, but that will give you plenty of time to get your account set up and some tours created. Some of the requirements needed to make this happen are verification and a background check. This is done to ensure that we have the safest and most secure group of guides as possible.</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <%= image_tag "accent_images/GuideNewAccount.jpg", alt:"product_screenshot", class:"w-[48rem] max-w-none rounded-xl shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-400/10 sm:w-[57rem] md:-ml-4 lg:-ml-0 py-4", width:"2432", height:"1442" %>
        <%= image_tag "accent_images/AccountAddress.jpg", alt:"product_screenshot", class:"w-[48rem] max-w-none rounded-xl shadow-xl ring-1 ring-gray-400/10 sm:w-[57rem] md:-ml-4 lg:-ml-0 py-4", width:"2432", height:"1442" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
